\pc \bd 186\bd*

\s Nisadiki Yesu Kristo
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Nisadiki Yesu Kristo sikuzote duniani, Hata na imani ndogo, nisadiki Yesu pekee.\bd*
\pc \bdit Nisadiki Yesu pekee, nisadiki sikuzote, Kati ya bahari gani, nisadiki Yesu pekee.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Roho yake anaagaza roho yangu njia zote, Nikifuata, sitaanguka, nisadiki Yesu pekee.\bd*
\pc \bdit Nisadiki Yesu pekee, nisadiki sikuzote, Kati ya bahari gani, nisadiki Yesu pekee.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ninaimba kwa furaha, ninaomba saa ya taabu, Kati ya habari vile, nisadiki Yesu pekee.\bd*
\pc \bdit Nisadiki Yesu pekee, nisadiki sikuzote, Kati ya bahari gani, nisadiki Yesu pekee.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Nisadiki hata mwisho wa uzima wangu hapa, Hata kwenda kwangu\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd , nisadiki Yesu pekee.\bd*
\pc \bdit Nisadiki Yesu pekee, nisadiki sikuzote, Kati ya bahari gani, nisadiki Yesu pekee.\bdit*
